title: I Made a Mistake...or Two
author: Jay & Sharon
description: I fell from a ladder and then this happened. It was crazy. I am still alive but I have a message I want to share with all the fellas. Ladies, feel free to share this with all your guy friends. Sharing is caring. Feel free to subscribe so you don't miss another life lesson.

localize.title: 間違いを犯してしまった...あるいは2つ
我犯了个错误......或两个错误
我犯了個錯誤......或兩個錯誤
